 regularly for updates on this page.\\n\\nUPDATE:  There will once again be a “meet & greet” before the first performance of the evening during which everyone attending the birthday performances will have the opportunity to meet members of the Estate team and their special guests for the evening.  In addition, Michael Bush will make a return visit to Las Vegas for the birthday celebration this year! He will be doing a book signing at the Michael Jackson ONE Boutique during the afternoon and will be one of the guests joining the Estate team during the pre-show “meet & greet”.  \\n\\nMore details on the book signing and other activities to come….\\n\\nUPDATE: This year, the main attraction of this highly anticipated event, which historically draws fans from all over the world, will be a special presentation by members of the cast of Michael Jackson ONE, created especially for the fans attending this year’s celebration. The performance begins with a one-time only performance to Michael’s #1 hit “Don’t Stop Til You Get Enough” which is not part of the regular Michael Jackson ONE show. This will be followed by a preview of two acts from the show - “Stranger In Moscow” and “Thriller”, consistently a crowd and critics favorite. And the special guests of the Estate this year include Michael Jackson ONE choreographers, Rich & Tone Talauega and Travis Payne. The schedule for the afternoon has also been confirmed:\\n\\n- 3:30 p.m. – Book signing with Michael Bush\\n- 4:00 p.m. – Special performance by Michael Jackson ONE performers followed by a Q&A with some of the cast members\\n- 5:30 p.m. – Meet-and-greet with the Estate and their invited guests\\n\\nCome celebrate the King of Pop’s birthday!\", \"is_canceled\": false, \"maybe_count\": 662, \"updated_time\": \"2015-08-20T21:09:06+0000\", \"attending_count\": 12323, \"interested_count\": 662}, {\"id\": \"787502441295264\", \"cover\": {\"id\": \"10152612498996473\", \"source\": \"https://scontent.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t31.0-8/s720x