ckage.\\n\\n- On the way out of the theater after seeing the documentary, stop in the Michael Jackson ONE Boutique for the book/DVD signings that starts at 3:15 pm.  Award winning director, Spike Lee, will be there to say hi to fans and to sign copies of the DVD of BAD25, the critically acclaimed documentary directed by Spike to celebrate Michael’s Bad album and the participating authors are:\\n    ->   Zack O’Malley Greenburg, whose new book Michael Jackson Inc. was released in June and offers a different perspective on Michael, the business person. \\n     ->   Joe Vogel, whose book Man In The Music, is an insightful and academic study of Michael’s music which Joe spent several years researching.\\n     ->   Michael Bush, whose book King of Style:  Dressing                           Michael Jackson offers fans a look at the creation of Michael’s wardrobe by the person who (along with his partner, Dennis Tompkins) worked with MJ for a quarter of a century.\\n\\n- More surprises to be announced.\\n\\nLearn more here: http://www.cirquedusoleil.com/mjbday\", \"is_canceled\": false, \"maybe_count\": 554, \"updated_time\": \"2014-08-18T16:09:05+0000\", \"attending_count\": 7704, \"interested_count\": 554}, {\"id\": \"627774083908425\", \"cover\": {\"id\": \"10151758054616473\", \"source\": \"https://scontent.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t31.0-8/s720x720/976061_10151758054616473_264561578_o.jpg?oh=e68ff7fa78d1480554a968c353dea241&oe=5A215615\", \"offset_x\": 0, \"offset_y\": 0}, \"place\": {\"id\": \"141444980659\", \"name\": \"Mandalay Bay Resort and Casino\", \"location\": {\"zip\": \"89119\", \"city\": \"Las Vegas\", \"state\": \"NV\", \"street\": \"3950 Las Vegas Blvd S\", \"country\": \"United States\", \"latitude\": 36.09212752717, \"longitude\": -115.17572960178}}, \"admins\": {\"data\": [{\"id\": \"19691681472\", \"pic_large\": \"https://scontent.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-1/p200x200/10868235_10153068640606473_3992284990222677775_n.jpg?oh=a1f0d872e76ddbec2402a8c1cbfd982b&oe=5A35617D\